procedures.name: Venipuncture

code.decode: Collection of venous blood by venipuncture

procedures.label: Blood Draw
procedures.description: Collection of venous blood for laboratory analysis, including Pharmacokinetics (PK), Pharmacodynamics (PD), hematology, clinical chemistry, serology, HbA1c, pregnancy test, FSH, and genetic sampling.

procedures.name: Urine Sample Collection
procedures.label: Urine Collection
procedures.description: Collection of urine samples for urinalysis, pregnancy test, and drug screening.

procedures.name: Vital Signs Monitoring
procedures.label: Vital Signs
procedures.description: Measurement of supine blood pressure, pulse rate, and body temperature at specified time points.

procedures.name: Electrocardiogram

code.decode: Electrocardiogram, routine ECG with at least 12 leads; with interpretation and report

procedures.label: ECG
procedures.description: Recording of single and triplicate 12-lead ECGs at specified time points.

procedures.name: Insulin Infusion
procedures.label: IV Insulin Infusion
procedures.description: Intravenous insulin infusion to induce hypoglycemia, stopped once bedside plasma glucose is <60 mg/dL.

procedures.name: Nasal Glucagon Administration
procedures.label: Nasal Glucagon Admin
procedures.description: Administration of 3 mg LY900018 via a single-use nasal dosing device.

procedures.name: Intramuscular Glucagon Injection

code.decode: Therapeutic, prophylactic, or diagnostic injection (specify substance or drug); subcutaneous or intramuscular

procedures.label: IM Glucagon Injection
procedures.description: Administration of 1 mg reconstituted intramuscular glucagon (IMG).

procedures.name: Bedside Plasma Glucose Monitoring
procedures.label: Bedside PG Monitoring
procedures.description: Frequent monitoring of plasma glucose levels using a bedside device for safety during hypoglycemia induction and post-treatment.

procedures.name: Height and Weight Measurement
procedures.label: Height and Weight
procedures.description: Measurement of patient's height at screening and weight at specified visits.

procedures.name: Injection-Site Assessment
procedures.label: Injection-Site Assessment
procedures.description: Assessment of the injection site for patients receiving intramuscular glucagon (IMG).

procedures.name: Nasal Inspection
procedures.label: Nasal Inspection
procedures.description: Inspection of the nasal passages for all patients at specified time points.

procedures.name: Edinburgh Hypoglycemia Scale
procedures.label: Hypoglycemia Questionnaire
procedures.description: Administration of the Edinburgh Hypoglycemia Scale questionnaire to evaluate recovery from clinical symptoms of hypoglycemia.

procedures.name: Intravenous Glucose Administration
procedures.label: IV Glucose
procedures.description: Administration of intravenous (IV) glucose as a safety provision if the patient experiences signs and symptoms of severe hypoglycemia requiring intervention.

medicalDevices.name: Nasal Dosing Device
medicalDevices.label: Nasal Glucagon Device
medicalDevices.description: A user-friendly, single-use, nasal dosing device that delivers 3 mg glucagon powder (LY900018).

medicalDevices.name: Syringe and Needle
medicalDevices.label: IM Injection Kit
medicalDevices.description: Device used for reconstitution and intramuscular injection of 1 mg glucagon (GlucaGen).

medicalDevices.name: IV Infusion Equipment
medicalDevices.label: IV Infusion Setup
medicalDevices.description: Equipment used for the intravenous infusion of insulin to induce hypoglycemia and for potential administration of rescue IV glucose.

medicalDevices.name: Bedside Glucose Monitor
medicalDevices.label: Glucose Meter
medicalDevices.description: Device for frequent bedside monitoring of plasma glucose (PG) levels for safety.

medicalDevices.name: 12-lead ECG Machine
medicalDevices.label: ECG Machine
medicalDevices.description: Device used to perform single and triplicate 12-lead electrocardiograms.

medicalDevices.name: Continuous Subcutaneous Insulin Infusion Pump
medicalDevices.label: CSII Pump
medicalDevices.description: An insulin pump used by some patients for their daily insulin therapy.
